  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Specifies the execution mode. In Audit mode, the system acts as if it is
            enforcing the access control policy, including emitting access denial
            entries in the logs but it does not actually deny any requests to host
            endpoints. In Enforce mode, the system will enforce the access control and
            it is the recommended mode of operation.
            </summary>
